After filling in the fields on the line with an item you want to sell, on the right there is a factbox that summarizes the empties in the document, calculated by the system based on the item quantity indicated on the lines:
<br>
     
<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000239-0/EN-EMPSalesOrder1.jpg"><br>
     
After posting the shipment, the empties are moved to the shipment.